  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The primary objective of this study is to investigate potential differences in treatment
      adherence by teenagers among four interventions during treatment for acne.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Same as above.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
