  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Adolescent subjects with a diagnosis of moderate to severe Acne vulgaris

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Subjects with acne conglobata, acne fulminans, secondary acne (chloracne,
             drug-induced acne, etc.), or severe acne requiring more than topical treatment (e.g.
             oral isotretinoin)
      </textblock>
